# Portal flash reel (`/investor/portal`) — same blob store as intro; upload `Investor Flash.mp4` here or override in Vercel.
NEXT_PUBLIC_INVESTOR_FLASH_VIDEO_URL=https://u7fkmtuvdvallnwg.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/Investor%20Flash.mp4
# Proposal overview intro — same blob; upload `Propsal Intro Video.mp4` (or override in Vercel).
